data.description: Beautiful home in desirable Wrights Mill S/D. This home is in a convenient location, minutes from Jackson Yacht Club, Natchez Trace, area dining and shopping.  Hardwood floors, tall ceilings, custom kitchen and large bedrooms are just a few of the upgraded features of this home. Step out back onto the covered patio and enjoy the private backyard. Wrights mill subdivision has nice amenities for the homeowner to enjoy such as a GORGEOUS community pool and gazebo/entertaining area. Go see this stylish home today!
